name: Number Place 10000
description:
Mind Training logic puzzle "Number Place"

The objective is to fill a 9x9 grid with numbers without repeatedly in all row, column and 3x3 squares.

10000 questions in 4 levels of difficulty from Easy to Expert.
Lets't choose question that suit yourself, or challenge harder with others!
